	"driver" is specified, instead of always set the disk type as
	"block".

2012-03-15  Alex Jia  <ajia@redhat.com>

	virsh: fix invalid free
	* tools/virsh.c (cmdDetachDisk): fix invalid free due to using
	  uninitialised value.

	* How to reproduce?
