2011-12-02  Eric Blake  <eblake@redhat.com>

	build: properly skip tests
	I got this failure on FreeBSD:

	shunloadtest.c: In function 'main':
	shunloadtest.c:150: error: 'EXIT_AM_SKIP' undeclared (first use in this function)

