	==25667==    by 0x804F14D: virtTestRun (testutils.c:140)

	* How to reproduce?
	% cd libvirt && ./configure && make && make -C tests valgrind
	or
	% valgrind -v --leak-check=full ./tests/virnettlscontexttest

