	Since directories can be used for <filesystem> passthrough, they are
	basically storage volumes.

	v2:
	    Skip ., .., lost+found dirs

	v3:
	    Use gnulib last_component

	v4:
	    Use gnulib "dirname.h", not system <dirname.h>
	    Don't skip lost+found

