	* tests/xmconfigdata/test-paravirt-vcpu.xml: Likewise.
	* tests/xml2sexprtest.c (mymain): New test.
	* tests/sexpr2xmltest.c (mymain): Likewise.
	* tests/xmconfigtest.c (mymain): Likewise.

