	* src/qemu/qemu_monitor.c, src/qemu/qemu_monitor.h: Add new
	  qemuMonitorGetMigrationStatus() command.
	* src/qemu/qemu_driver.c: Use new qemuMonitorGetMigrationStatus()
	  command to check completion status.

