2009-09-15  Daniel P. Berrange  <berrange@redhat.com>

	Fix dlopen of secrets driver
	* src/Makefile.am: Add gnulib.la for base64 functions
	* src/libvirt_private.syms: Export virFileNameMatchesSuffix

